   <taskbody>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Perform the following checks before starting up the metering conveyor scale:</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Inspect the metering conveyor scale for visible damage, and correct any problems
                  before operating.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Verify that the safety mechanisms are installed and in proper condition.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Verify that the rotary survey is installed and functioning correctly.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Verify that the feed and discharge unit is connected correctly.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Make sure that no personnel are present in the danger area or in the areas of
                     movement of machine parts.</li>
               </ul>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To turn on the metering conveyor scale:</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Switch the lockable main switch to On.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Acknowledge the emergency stop using the operating screen.</li>
               </ul>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To turn off the metering conveyor scale:</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Use the user interface at the control cabinet.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">The metering conveyor scale continues to run and terminates the movements of
                     the actuators.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Then switch off the metering conveyor scale using the lockable main switch.  </li>
               </ul>
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                     <image href="media/image6.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            align="center"
                            class="- topic/image "/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">If a fault or malfunction occurs, this is indicated at the user interface.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <note type="note" class="- topic/note ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">For information about possible errors and malfunctions and the procedure for
                     eliminating errors, see the electrical documentation. </p>
               </note>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
   </taskbody>
